def-group:


    Set Boot Loader Superuser Username to Unique Value
    {{{- oval_affected(products) }}}
    The grub2 boot loader superuser should have a username that is hard to guess.



    {{{ oval_file_absent_criterion("/boot/grub2/grub.cfg", rule_id + "_grub_cfg") }}}




{{{ oval_file_absent("/boot/grub2/grub.cfg", rule_id + "_grub_cfg") }}}





  /boot/grub2/grub.cfg
  ^[\s]*set[\s]+superusers="(?i)(?!root|admin|administrator)(?-i).*"$
  1
